title: #92Noon! Birk/Siny/Bercich/Lavelle!
description: Back on our feet again! Montage following the Vikings win yesterday, Birk and Dave Sinykin both join for opinions, Bercich in studio with takes and analysis from the game, The Drive highlights the most impactful Vikings drive from the win in Houston, and Lavelle is in studio to close the show!
